    "Qiju granules were extracted and purified from Rhodiola rosea L.",
    "[Crassulaceae], Portulaca oleracea L..",
    "Placebo granules were purified from dextrin and caramel, with their appearance being identical and taste being similar to Qiju granules.",
    "The granules were stored at room temperature.",
    "Participants in the Qiju and control groups were instructed to dissolve 1 package of granules (15 g) in warm drinking water and take them orally every morning throughout the study period."
